comments: Smart (MEM) cleanly dislodges the ball from Williamson (NOP) during his driving shot attempt.
Smart (MEM) deflects the incoming inbounds pass intended for Valanciunas (NOP).
The ball is last touched by Smart (MEM) prior to it going out of bounds.

Murphy III (NOP) initiates illegal contact with Smart (MEM) that causes him to trip.  After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that the foul does not meet the criteria for a clear path foul.
Murphy III (NOP) establishes himself in Smart's (MEM) path and absorbs the incoming contact from Smart (MEM) during the screen.
Smart (MEM) lowers his arm and marginal contact occurs with Ingram's (NOP) arm that does not affect his intended pass.
Tillman (MEM) moves alongside Williamson's (NOP) path and the body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Valanciunas (NOP) initiates contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) establishes himself in Bane's (MEM) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact from Bane during the screen.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly engages and then disengages from Valanciunas (NOP) during the rebound.

Morant (MEM) blocks the shot attempt after the ball makes contact with the backboard and has a chance to score.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending is confirmed.
Ingram (NOP) loses control of the ball as it is briefly pinned to his body, which he legally recovers prior to releasing his pass.
Bane (MEM) cleanly blocks McCollum's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) does not release the shot attempt prior to the expiration of the shot clock.

Replay review of the foul called on Jones (NOP) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Jones makes contact to Morant's (MEM) arm after the release of his driving shot attempt, which is marginal.  Neither team has possession of the ball at the time of the whistle and play resumes with a jump ball.
Murphy III (NOP) makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Smart's (MEM) hand on the ball.  The ensuing body contact during the loose ball is incidental.

Replay review of the foul called on Valanciunas (NOP) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. 
 Valanciunas jumps back into Jackson Jr. (MEM) and reaches across his shoulder, initiating illegal contact.  The illegal contact occurs prior to the ball being touched and therefore, the game clock is reset to 00:00.4.
Jones (NOP) makes incidental contact with Smart's (MEM) body as he's pivoting.
Williamson (NOP) moves alongside Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and although he lowers his arm during the shot attempt, the contact is marginal.
Morant (MEM) contests Murphy III's (NOP) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Williamson (NOP) makes contact with the ball while he is out of bounds.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before releasing his driving shot attempt.
Daniels (NOP) places a hand on Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) body during his shooting motion but the contact is marginal.
Smart (MEM) establishes a legal guarding position outside of the RA and in Williamson's (NOP) path when the contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
The ball is last touched by Bane (MEM) prior to it going out of bounds.
Smart (MEM) initiates contact with McCollum's (NOP) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Daniels (NOP) makes clean contact to the ball as Morant (MEM) receives the inbounds pass.
McCollum (NOP) commits a take foul on Smart (MEM).
Daniels (NOP) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM).
